constant
Element


constant
&constant.purpose;


&constant.synopsis.gen;
Description



A Constant identifies a value as immutable. It is most often
used to identify system limitations or other defined constants.


Processing expectations


&format.inline;




&constant.parents.gen;
&constant.children.gen;

Attributes

class



Class identifies constants that are system
or application limits (for example, the maximum length of a filename).





